# ---- Datasets & trained models (NEVER commit — regenerated by the training scripts) ----
# Broad patterns on purpose: don't enumerate specific dataset filenames. Curated INPUTS
# that SHOULD be tracked are re-included explicitly with '!' below.
*.xlsx
*.parquet
*.tsv
*.csv
*.onnx
*.pkl
*.joblib
*.pt
*.ckpt
*_models/
odor_model/
# ...but DO track the small, hand-curated input lists:
!flavor_volatiles.csv

